quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,Demi dum rasul nyang malaikat Nyang ba haba got keu hamba Allah
  77,2,Teureubang meutreung tajam ban kilat
  77,3,Geujakba rahmat keu alam luah
  77,4,Geupeungkleh nyang got nibak nyang jeuheut
  77,5,Geupeutroh ligat teuma peurintah
  77,6,Na nyang Neuampon uleh Hadharat Ladom peuingat haba geupeugah
  77,7,Keubit roe teuma peue nyang geujanji Han jeuet han jadi lagee geupeugah Peue nyang geujanji bak gata bandum
  77,8,Watee bintang dum ka abeh sudah
  77,9,Langet ka teuhah han sapeue na le
  77,10,Gunong dum reule anco ngon bicah
  77,11,Bak rasul-rasul ka geubri watee
  77,12,Uroe peue teuntee tanggoh geupeugah
  77,13,Sampoe troh uroe putosan Tuhan
  77,14,Peue roe uroe nyan jeuet teuh tapeugah
  77,15,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,16,Kon ka beh dilee meupeubinasa Bandum ka nyata masa nyang sudah
  77,17,Kamoe peuikot dudoe nibak nyan Lagee ureueng nyan cit pubuet salah
  77,18,Meunan keuh Kamoe ‘oh meukeurija Ureueng meudacha bandum meubalah
  77,19,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,20,Kon Kamoe peujeut gata nyoe bandum Bak ie nyang maklum hina sileupah
  77,21,Meukeubah ie nyan bak teumpat teutap
  77,22,Padum trep meuhat Kamoe boh batah
  77,23,Ban nyang h‘eut Kamoe Kamoe boh kada Sineujroh kada nyang Kamoe ulah
  77,24,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Soe nyang kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,25,Kon bak meusapat meupeujeuet bumoe
  77,26,Nyang udep sinoe sang seunang leupah Meunan pih sinoe dum ureueng mate
  77,27,Gunong deungon gle sinan meukeubah Gunong nyang meugah meubri ngon ujeuen Keu gata bandum ie jih gleh leupah
  77,28,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,29,Jak keudeh bandum bek le tapeutrep Nyang takheun sulet keunan talangkah
  77,30,Jak laju keunan u yup bak kayee Na cabeung jih Ihee cit trang sileupah
  77,31,Kon jeut meureului di yup kayee nyan Tutong di sinan hanaban peugah
  77,32,Jirhom meuk apui be-be meuligoe
  77,33,Unta sang bagoe kuneng sileupah
  77,34,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,35,Jih dum uroe nyoe han jeut marit le
  77,36,Han geuizin le meungaku salah
  77,37,Uroe nyan teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah
  77,38,Nyoe keuh uroe nyoe uroe putosan Ngon gata bandum meusapat sudah Ngon ureueng dilee bandum meusapat
  77,39,Peue ek na pakat Lon nyoe tahilah
  77,40,Uroe nyoe teuma ceulaka keubit Ureueng kheun sulet keu rasul Allah